high_descs: Head straight into the other room, turn right at the chair, head to the TV.
Pick up the credit card on the bottom shelf of the TV stand.
Turn right, bring the card to the chair next to the tall lamp.
Put the card on the left chair.
Go back to the TV stand on your left.
Pick up the credit card on the TV stand.
Turn right, go to the left chair.
Put the credit card on the chair, left of the other credit card.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards on a chair.

high_descs: Go forward and around the furniture to the front of the TV stand on the right.
Pick up the blue credit card on the bottom shelf of the stand.
Turn right and move towards the gray arm chair on the left.
Place the credit card on the seat.
Turn around and move back to the front of the TV stand.
Pick up the blue credit card on the left of the TV.
Turn right and go back to the gray arm chair on the left.
Place the credit card on the left of the first credit card.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards from the TV stand to the chair.

high_descs: Go across the room to the coffee table, then turn right and go forward to the entertainment center.
Pick up the credit card from the shelf under the TV.
Turn right to face the chair, next to the lamp.
Put the credit card on the chair.
Turn around and return to the entertainment center.
Pick up the credit card on the entertainment center.
Turn right to face the chair, next to the lamp.
Put the credit card on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Moved two credit cards to the chair.
